lor: rgb(255, 153, 0); ">清香爽口</span>，营养丰富。西洋菜的营养物质比较全面，其中超氧化物岐化酶(即SOD)的含量很高，还含有丰富的维生素及矿物质。具有清燥润肺、化痰止咳、利尿等功效。益脑健身的保健蔬菜。</strong></strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 24px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); "><strong>食用方法：先将西洋菜干用热水浸软，然后与其它材料煲汤或炖汤</strong><strong>。</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 24px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); "><strong>1、<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0); ">西洋菜干炖鱼头汤</span>：西洋菜干50克，浸软，大鱼头1个，蜜枣2个，加水适量，炖2-3个小时，调味即可成为一款营养、美味的靓汤。</strong></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size: 24px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); "><strong>2、<span style="background-color: rgb(255, 153, 0); ">西洋菜猪骨蜜枣汤</span>：西洋菜干50克，蜜枣6个，猪骨200克，加水适量，慢火煲2-3个小时，调味后即可食用。</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-size: 24px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); "><img align="absMiddle" src="http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/747145118/T2HeqeXhJaXXXXXXXX_!!747145118.jpg" alt="" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; " /></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-size: 36px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); ">质地脆嫩多汁</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; ">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center; "><span style="font-size: 24px; "><span style="font-family: lisu; "><span style="color: rgb(40, 122, 0); "><img align="absMiddle" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/747145118/T2tveeXdNXXXXXXXXX_!!747145118.jpg" alt="" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; bor