tial initial; " class="tshop-psm ke-post J_DetailSection" id="description">\r\n<div style="width: 750px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; " id="J_DivItemDesc" class="content">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 广州特产/从化特产华隆龙眼干<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 采用广州从化特产-优质无公害龙眼为原料，经精心挑选后用现代先进干燥工艺及微波杀菌技术精制而成。产品皮薄肉厚核小，果肉金黄、香甜爽滑，龙眼风味浓郁，是传统桂圆干难于比拟的。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙</strong><strong>眼干又称桂圆干，是深受广大消费者欢迎的营养滋补品，在我国各地均有很大的消费市场。龙眼果实中含有50%&mdash;70%的水分，又含有各种营养物质，如糖、蛋白质、维生素等。龙眼干的焙制，是借助热力作用将果实中的水分降低到一定限度，使其可溶性物质的浓度提高到微生物难以利用的程度，所以可以进行较长时间的保存。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【功效】<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1、补血益气：适宜肤色没有光华，失去红润、手脚冰冷的人群</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>　　2、提高免疫力：蛋白质是维持免疫机能最重要的营养素，为构成白血球和抗体的主要成份。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>　　3、安神除烦：钙的作用可用来放松肌肉和神经，从而使身心放松，避免紧张不安、焦躁易怒。帮助入睡。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>　　4、健脾：适用于脾气虚弱，运化无力所致的脘腹胀满，大便溏泄，食欲不振，肢倦乏力等症。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>　　5、养颜护肤：增强皮肤张力、消除皱纹的功效。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>　　6、抗衰抗辐射：具有极强的清除自由基的能力，有抗辐射、预防心脑血管疾病、提高免疫力、延缓衰老等功效。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 食用方法：剥壳后即食或炖汤、煲汤、煲粥、泡茶。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 净重量500克</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; text-align: center; "><strong><img align="absMiddle" alt="" style="border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: top; " src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/747145118/T2w90_XbJbXXXXXXXX_!!747145118.jpg" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</