; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;1000">重量(g):&nbsp;1000</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;中国大陆">产地:&nbsp;中国大陆</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;广东">食品特产产地:&nbsp;广东</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="clear: both; margin-bottom: 20px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font: normal normal normal 14px/1.5 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; display: block; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " class="tshop-psm ke-post J_DetailSection" id="description">\r\n<div style="width: 750px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; " id="J_DivItemDesc" class="content">\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>荔枝乃领南佳果，享誉中外，历代文人墨客赞不绝口，其蜜，昧醇厚、芳香浓郁，品之有荡气国肠之感既有</strong></div>\r\n<div><strong>蜂蜜之清润，却因为酿蜜时添加了各种蜜蜂自己特有的成分，故无荔枝之燥热，但其特殊的生津、益血、理气、润心爽目、解渴生津、理气散寒、补血补气之功效，是岭南特有的蜜种。</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 广州特产/从化特产国强荔枝蜜遇上阴雨天的时候，荔枝蜜会比较稀，水分比较多；天气晴好的时候，荔枝蜜比较浓稠，香味也更加明显。</strong></div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 保质期：12个月<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;净含量：1Kg</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201209/thumb_img/524_thumb_G_1348542107769.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/524_G_1362475819607.jpg', 'images/201209/source_img/524_P_1348542107659.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1348481754, 436, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1354525954, 0, '', -1, -1, 3, NULL),
(597, 178, 'YHG212-121206', '无籽红提', '', '+', 0, 14, '', 998, 0.000, 62.40, 52.00, 0.00, 0, 0, 1, '', '', '<p>&nbsp;商品介绍：</p>\r\n<div>南非无籽红提外表呈圆珠型，色泽深红，果粒大小均匀、着生松紧适度，皮薄肉厚，味甜爽脆。</div>\r\n<div>有易果装和小包装可供选择。&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>特殊说明：</div>\r\n<div>若提子成熟度、甜度略高，有个别掉粒属正常现象，但不影响口感。</div>\r\n<div>储存方式：&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>适宜放在0℃-1℃冷藏，先将有损伤的丢弃，放入有孔的塑料袋于冰箱中保存，大约可存放一周。&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>商品禁忌&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>糖尿病患者，便秘者，脾胃虚寒者，少食&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>忌与海鲜、鱼、萝卜、四环素同食，服用人参者忌食&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>吃后不能立刻喝水，易引发腹泻&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>商品文化</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;红提，又名晚红、红地球、红提子，属欧亚种，原产于美国加州，是由美国加利福尼亚州立大学于70年代进行杂交试验，培育而成的一个葡萄品种。我国1987年引入该品种。</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;推荐菜谱</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;橙味提子蛋糕卷&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>主料：低筋面粉100克，鸡蛋5个，白砂糖100克，色拉油75ml，橙汁100ml 辅料：提子干50克&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>1：提子干提前用温水泡软，沥干水分备用；鸡蛋分开蛋黄与蛋白，分别用无油无水的干净容器装好；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>2：橙汁与色拉油混合搅拌至看不见明显的油星；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>3：加入已经过筛2次的低粉，不用过多搅拌，只要拌至看不见干粉即可；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>4：加入蛋黄，搅拌至顺滑，放在旁边备用；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>5：蛋白中加入几滴白醋，低速打至粗泡，分三次加入白砂糖，中速打至湿性发泡；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>6：分三次把蛋白霜与蛋黄糊拌匀，用从下往上翻拌、切拌的方式，不能划圈；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>7：加入提子干，拌匀，把面糊倒进铺了油纸的烤盘，在桌上振几下，振出气泡；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>8：烤盘放进已经预热好170度的烤箱，中上层，165度，上下火，烤25~30分钟，出炉倒扣，趁热撕开油纸；&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>9：稍凉后利用擀面杖卷起，彻底放凉后切件。&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', 'images/201210/thumb_img/597_thumb_G_1350371549154.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/597_G_1362475819368.jpg', 'images/201210/source_img/597_P_1350371549112.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1352944615, 212, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1354783658, 0, '', -1, -1, 2, NULL);
