arial, 宋体, sans-serif; display: block; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " class="tshop-psm ke-post J_DetailSection" id="description">\r\n<div style="width: 750px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; " id="J_DivItemDesc" class="content">\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>荔枝盛产南方，被誉为&ldquo;果中之王&rdquo;。荔枝蜜是我国南方地区生产的上等蜂蜜，颜色为琥珀色，芳香馥郁，带有浓烈的荔枝花香味。主要分布于我国华南地区，如广东、福建、广西等省。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 荔枝蜜采用荔枝之花蜜，气息芳香馥郁，味甘甜，微带荔枝果酸味，既有蜂蜜之清润，却因为蜜蜂酿蜜时添加了各种蜜蜂自己特有的成分，故无荔枝之燥热，但其特殊的生津、益血、理气、之功效，是岭南特有的蜜种，馈赠远方亲友，&ldquo;不辞长作岭南人&rdquo;的特等蜂蜜。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 净重量：1.5公斤</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201209/thumb_img/533_thumb_G_1348538603232.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/533_G_1362475835734.jpg', 'images/201209/source_img/533_P_1348538604430.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1348538603, 464, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1354525917, 0, '', -1, -1, 3, NULL),
