dding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;2150g">规格:&nbsp;2150g</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;2150">重量(g):&nbsp;2150</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;中国大陆">产地:&nbsp;中国大陆</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;广东">食品特产产地:&nbsp;广东</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="clear: both; margin-bottom: 20px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font: normal normal normal 14px/1.5 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; display: block; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " class="tshop-psm ke-post J_DetailSection" id="description">\r\n<div style="width: 750px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; " id="J_DivItemDesc" class="content">\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;本礼盒由精选荔枝蜜、纯冬蜜（鸭脚木蜜）、荷花花粉三大品种组成，堪称润至园蜂产品之精品</strong></div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 一、 荷花花粉??蜂花粉之王<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 美国康乃尔大学摩尔斯教授对荷花粉的研究指出：荷花花粉营养成分高于任何花粉，有丰富的氨基酸，总量24.2%以上，其中人体必需八种氨基酸含量均高。有益于人体的常量元素、维生素最齐全而且较高，特别是油质中的不饱和脂肪酸含量为任何花粉所不及。对美容、强身、益肾、增智、病后康复等，其功效高于任何花粉。荷花又称莲花、芙蓉，处于污泥而不染。&ldquo;芙蓉花发满江红&rdquo;，&ldquo;阵阵荷香扫闷雷&rdquo;给唐代的一位女名人&ldquo;柔肌信有香&rdquo;的艳体，&ldquo;芳荷朵朵玉无瑕，蕊粉柔香益万家，底事观音招众目，缘由食粉座莲花&rdquo;。</strong></div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二、 从化荔枝蜜<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 从化市是中国荔枝蜜原生态基地，盛产优质荔枝蜜（桂味、糯米糍花蜜），品质上乘，既有蜂蜜之清润，却无荔枝之燥热，是荔枝之精华。现代名作杨朔写下脍炙人口佳作《荔枝蜜》。&ldquo;日尝荔蜜三十滴，不枉此生岭南人&rdquo;。</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三、 纯冬蜜（鸭脚木蜜）<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 蜜蜂采自深山老林冬季开花泌蜜的鸭脚木花蜜酿造而成，纯天然无任何污染，香味浓郁、清热解毒、调理保健肠胃，兼具醒酒益智、清热咳、润燥，是男女老少一年四季的保健佳品。</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201209/thumb_img/535_thumb_G_1348539143583.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/535_G_1362475837995.jpg', 'images/201209/source_img/535_P_1348539143542.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1348539143, 469, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1354525905, 0, '', -1, -1, 3, NULL);
