 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;1000">重量(g):&nbsp;1000</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;中国大陆">产地:&nbsp;中国大陆</li>\r\n    <li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; float: left; width: 206px; height: 24px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; text-indent: 5px; line-height: 24px; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis; " title="&nbsp;广东">食品特产产地:&nbsp;广东</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="clear: both; margin-bottom: 20px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font: normal normal normal 14px/1.5 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; display: block; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " class="tshop-psm ke-post J_DetailSection" id="description">\r\n<div style="width: 750px; padding-top: 10px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; word-wrap: break-word; " id="J_DivItemDesc" class="content">\r\n<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>蜂蜜被誉为天然的玉液琼浆，以其晶莹、清香、富有神韵，数千年来倍受青睐，在古代蜂蜜为皇室贡品。蜂蜜含有葡萄糖、氨基酸、矿物质、酶、有机酸等营养成分，更因其天然纯正而成为现代人们不可多得的绿色食品，是您送礼、自奉的最佳选择。</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【龙眼蜜】</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;龙眼蜜主要分布于我国华南地区，如广东、广西、福建等省，蜜色呈琥珀色，食味甘甜，不易结晶，具有浓烈的龙眼的香气，在我国单花蜜中其蛋白质含量最高，达1.699%。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 广州特产/从化特产国强龙眼蜜它有养血安神、开胃益脾、养颜、清热润燥、补中益气之功效，对心脾血虚引起的心悸不安、失眠和记忆力减退有辅助疗效。特别适合女性食用。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 现代医学临床应用证明，蜂蜜可促进消化吸收，增进食欲，镇静安眠，提高机体抵抗力，对促进婴幼儿的生长发育有着积极作用。蜂蜜几乎含有蔬菜中的全部营养成分。在冬季每天喝上3&mdash;4汤匙蜂蜜，既补充营养，又可保证大便通畅。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 【鸭脚木蜜】</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 国强鸭脚木蜜：源于中药树种鸭脚木花蜜，是岭南特有冬季蜜种。故俗称&ldquo;冬蜜&rdquo;。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 广州特产/从化特产润至园鸭脚木蜜色泽为浅琥珀色，较易结晶，质地优良，味甘而略带特有苦味。除具有蜂蜜之清热、补中、解毒、润燥等功效外，还有发汗解表，能风除湿之功效，对感冒发热，咽喉肿痛，风湿关节痛，心脏病、肝脏病、高血压、胃及十二指肠溃疡、关节炎、神经系统疾病有较好辅助疗效。是带有中药特色的蜂蜜品种，深受东南亚地区人们喜爱。</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 1.12em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.12em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; "><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 龙眼蜜（500g）+ 荔枝干 + 鸭脚木蜜（500g）</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201209/thumb_img/551_thumb_G_1348541099191.jpg', 'images/201303/goods_img/551_G_1362475850526.jpg', 'images/201209/source_img/551_P_1348541099791.jpg', 1, '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 1348541099, 429, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1354525805, 0, '', -1, -1, 3, NULL),
